short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get notified when it's not just them in your google meet call.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When you're about to join a Google Meet call, an extra button will popup on the page asking you if you would like to be notified when someone else joins the call. Click the button and then once another person joins the call you will get a chrome notification that you can use to click back to the meet call for you to join!
